I had decided not to forgive anyone
who would harm Neferu-sama, but...

rows.label: qst105709_msg0002

...why is it that I cannot
bring myself to hate them...

rows.label: qst105709_msg0003
rows.name:
Were you moved by their
parental affection, Wadatsumi?

rows.label: qst105709_msg0005
rows.name:
Nopon are small and adorable
like Neferu-sama...

rows.label: qst105709_msg0006
rows.name:
Is this person alright, mo?
Nopon are adorable, but these
ones are villains, mo.

rows.label: qst105709_msg0007
rows.name:
...I shall make a note
of this in my diary.
